  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Morsel-driven parallel full scan + filter on l_shipdate (60M rows → 59M after filter). Use thread-local hash aggregation on (returnflag, linestatus) with 6 groups. Vectorized filtering with SIMD for numeric aggregates. Final merge + sort trivial (6 tuples).",
